Go for a long walk , around your neighborhood or in a store or in a mall . I know this l sounds so random and so simple but I went through some really depressing sad things in my life and I went for a walk and to this day I can’t tell you how much going for a walk literally kept me sane and from spiraling out of control try it every day and for a while it won’t feel like it’s working until you realize that you’re out there in nature or you’re walking near people .
